{"tid":1371697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗黑夜】新片段曝光！　白衣人追打車廂市民　發射塑膠彈","createTime":"2019-07-27T09:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T10:02:39.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"420ef3c198c5e4d8ed606212a6820cc6ef666e09","tid":1371697,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"[url]blob:<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/04c0880c-523d-4fcc-b1e8-426a02c7a368[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F04c0880c-523d-4fcc-b1e8-426a02c7a368%5B%2Furl%5D&d=YoMLTdJ4KFDt7wuWjEYT122%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=ca93c088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/04c0880c-523d-4fcc-b1e8-426a02c7a368[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗於昨晚（21日）經歷黑暗一夜，社工黃先生（化名）在被白衣人襲擊的西鐵車廂，經歷了畢生難忘的8分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n黃先生當時目擊一群白衣人襲擊市民。從黃先生傳給香港01記者的片段，站於月台的白衣人以武器無差別襲擊車廂內市民，<span style=\"color: red;\">其間更有人用氣槍將一些塑膠彈射入車廂，為時約十數秒。</span><br />\n<br />\n片段顯示，車廂的市民不斷狂呼大叫：「有老有細，唔好打。」有白衣人用棍指着乘客：「唔好再嚟元朗。」當時，車廂內的人最希望列車關門開車，但不知何故，列車關門後，數度再打開，白衣人再次補棍。列車真正開動後，乘客才真正離開「人間煉獄」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3065625/org/55420b43fe78c55d220839cee2a8a1c3.jpg/rpWMiXSnOO7KURgsyHiSsyFStIh6L_SEJhQkTAwUJEw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3065625%2Forg%2F55420b43fe78c55d220839cee2a8a1c3.jpg%2FrpWMiXSnOO7KURgsyHiSsyFStIh6L_SEJhQkTAwUJEw&h=ba082946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n居於新界西的黃先生昨晚從區內社交媒體得悉，元朗區有白衣人聚眾可能生事，打算協助當區居民。他於晚上9時許到達元朗雞地（Yoho Town旁），於鳳攸北街公園看到有逾百名白衣人聚集，約一半人手持藤條並綁着國旗。<br />\n<br />\n黃先生即時單人走上西鐵元朗站，已發現有兩名不相識的社工在場。黃稱，已有人帶來數十件上衣到場，擱在出入口的扶手。他們一同勸喻穿黑衣者改穿其他顏色的上衣才出閘，並避免行往雞地的方向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3065654/org/67907eceb92e57d050cbf1033cd4d01c.jpg/x4TPmqrnQElBG9EdJII0gBI0koBu2ClCF4Xc4ReF3OE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3065654%2Forg%2F67907eceb92e57d050cbf1033cd4d01c.jpg%2Fx4TPmqrnQElBG9EdJII0gBI0koBu2ClCF4Xc4ReF3OE&h=70db05f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n數分鐘後，一大班白衣人到達元朗站，先襲擊個別市民，並衝上月台。黃先生亦衝上月台走入車廂，協助市民。從黃先生拍得的片段，其間有人大叫：「有老有細，唔好打！」車廂內不斷傳出：「痴線㗎！」、「關車呀！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3064905/org/8e948c542b28fbe3f69a4965c647dafe.jpg/0RrMCZM6XPcUFsKTPNop4a7YB8J_0L0LZoKsbGaCrGw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3064905%2Forg%2F8e948c542b28fbe3f69a4965c647dafe.jpg%2F0RrMCZM6XPcUFsKTPNop4a7YB8J_0L0LZoKsbGaCrGw&h=800f3792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n襲擊期間 白色塑膠彈射入車廂<br />\n<br />\n片段顯示，白衣人襲擊期間，有白色的塑膠彈不斷從月台射入，有乘客被射中後，按着頭驚叫：「乜黎㗎」。黃先生表示，膠彈射入期間，乘客都很驚慌，他很驚被射傷眼。及後他於車廂發現，有多顆比BB彈稍大一點的塑膠彈在車廂地面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3064903/org/2b54911bdccd6fae936f6057f124c0f0.jpg/sE39qs5uNP3xZoPa8j8ltHzyOeG1fVw5-gjtLtAI7S4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3064903%2Forg%2F2b54911bdccd6fae936f6057f124c0f0.jpg%2FsE39qs5uNP3xZoPa8j8ltHzyOeG1fVw5-gjtLtAI7S4&h=cf981d46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如屍殺列車  車門關上再開 白衣人補棍<br />\n<br />\n黃先生表示，「站在我前三排的阿伯，俾人打爆頭，我隔籬阿婆踎低，保護阿伯。」折騰約十分鐘，車門終於關上後，乘客之後商討如何協助傷者，有人說「屯門有急症室」，並商討如何合作帶傷者到急症室。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3064893/org/b0fd10fb3c1add2dd1fb1e09c639b861.jpg/MEZKSnSXO9bgeSetVza7_XAbwHG37nJtqWIYT6liGE8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3064893%2Forg%2Fb0fd10fb3c1add2dd1fb1e09c639b861.jpg%2FMEZKSnSXO9bgeSetVza7_XAbwHG37nJtqWIYT6liGE8&h=4346205a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃先生稱，他形容這經歷如電影「屍殺列車」，尤其是列車多次都關不上門，感覺如「等死」。"},{"pid":"ad15ce09a2965972aa484b64a2c2b7a36272b359","tid":1371697,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"大量P牌五毛帶風向叫人留低同黑警對峙<br />\n<br />\n大家快撤退"},{"pid":"a99f21600d5494d51d979932e74ce4633327129c","tid":1371697,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}